file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: WhatsClubb OpenAPI
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3001'

paths:
  /users/me:
    get:
      tags:
        - Users
      summary: "Get current authenticated user"
      responses: { }

  /login/password:
    post:
      tags:
        - Login
      summary: "Login with email and password"
      responses: { }

  /login/mfa/phone-otp:
    post:
      tags:
        - Login
      summary: "MFA login with OTP"
      responses: { }

  /login/qr/sessions:
    post:
      tags:
        - QR Login
      summary: "Create QR login session"
      responses: { }

  /login/qr/sessions/{sessionId}:
    put:
      tags:
        - QR Login
      summary: "Accept or reject QR login"
      responses: { }

  /login/qr/sessions/{sessionId}/events:
    get:
      tags:
        - QR Login
      summary: "Subscribe on session events"
      responses: { }
